# Chakra UI v3

This project uses **Chakra UI v3** which has significant API changes from v2.

## MCP Server Available

Use the `project-0-tv-minder-chakra-ui` MCP server for Chakra docs:

- `get_component_example` - Get component usage examples
- `get_component_props` - Get component props
- `v2_to_v3_code_review` - Review code for v2→v3 migration issues

## Key v3 Patterns

### Compound Components

Components use dot notation (not separate imports):

```tsx
// ✅ v3
<Tabs.Root>
  <Tabs.List>
    <Tabs.Trigger value="one">Tab 1</Tabs.Trigger>
  </Tabs.List>
  <Tabs.Content value="one">Content</Tabs.Content>
</Tabs.Root>

// ❌ v2 (don't use)
<Tabs>
  <TabList>
    <Tab>Tab 1</Tab>
  </TabList>
  <TabPanels>
    <TabPanel>Content</TabPanel>
  </TabPanels>
</Tabs>
```

### Color Palette

Use `colorPalette` prop instead of `colorScheme`:

```tsx
// ✅ v3
<Button colorPalette="cyan">Click</Button>

// ❌ v2
<Button colorScheme="cyan">Click</Button>
```

### Semantic Tokens

Use semantic color tokens:

- `fg.muted` for muted text
- `whiteAlpha.100`, `whiteAlpha.400` for borders/overlays
- `blackAlpha.800` for dark overlays

### No ChakraProvider

Use the custom `Provider` from `~/components/ui/provider.tsx` which wraps theme config.

## Padding and Margin Units

Use numbers like `4` or `8` instead of `16px` or `32px`.

```tsx
// ✅ v3
<Box p="4">Content</Box>

// ❌ v2
<Box p="16px">Content</Box>
```
